    {
      "id": "el_17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 419,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "N = D x Q + R  (0 <= R < D)\nDividend = Divisor x Quotient + Remainder\n\nSame remainder R with D1,D2:\n  N - R divisible by LCM(D1,D2)\n  N = LCM(D1,D2) x k + R\n\nWHY: N-R is divisible by both D1 and D2\n  So N-R must be a multiple of LCM(D1,D2)\n\nEx: N÷5 rem 3, N÷7 rem 3 → N-3 div by LCM(5,7)=35\n  Smallest N=38: 38/5=7r3✓ 38/7=5r3✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 17,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "N = D x Q + R  (0 <= R < D)\nDividend = Divisor x Quotient + Remainder\n\nSame remainder R with D1,D2:\n  N - R divisible by LCM(D1,D2)\n  N = LCM(D1,D2) x k + R\n\nWHY: N-R is divisible by both D1 and D2\n  So N-R must be a multiple of LCM(D1,D2)\n\nEx: N÷5 rem 3, N÷7 rem 3 → N-3 div by LCM(5,7)=35\n  Smallest N=38: 38/5=7r3✓ 38/7=5r3✓",
      "autoResize": true,
