      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let (a-2), a, (a+2)\n  Sum=3a=93 → a=31\nStep 2: Numbers: 29, 31, 33\n  Check: 29+31+33=93✓\n\nTRICK (middle number):\nMiddle = Sum/n = 93/3 = 31\nThen subtract/add the gap(2)\n\n  29 ── 31 ── 33\n    +2    +2\n\nNatural: gap=1 | Even/Odd: gap=2\n\nAnswer: 29, 31, 33 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
