      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: List N mod 5=3: 3,8,13,18,23...\n  List N mod 7=4: 4,11,18,25...\n  First match = 18\nStep 2: Check: 18/5=3r3✓ 18/7=2r4✓\n\nTRICK (list & match):\nList shorter cycle, check other condition\nN mod 7=4: 4,11,18... check 18 mod 5=3✓\n\nGeneral: N = 18+LCM(5,7)k = 18+35k\nAll solutions: 18, 53, 88...\n\nAnswer: Smallest N = 18 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
