    {
      "id": "el_66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1580,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=(50+16)/2=33, S=(50-16)/2=17\nStep 2: Product = 33×17 = 561\n\nTRICK (direct formula):\nProduct = (S²-D²)/4\n= (2500-256)/4 = 2244/4 = 561\nSkips finding the actual numbers!\n\n  |◄──── 50 (sum) ────►|\n  |◄─ 17 ─►|◄── 33 ──►|\n\nAnswer: Product = 561 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
