        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: L=(50+16)/2=33, S=(50-16)/2=17\nStep 2: Product = 33×17 = 561\n\nTRICK (direct formula):\nProduct = (S²-D²)/4\n= (2500-256)/4 = 2244/4 = 561\nSkips finding the actual numbers!\n\n  |◄──── 50 (sum) ────►|\n  |◄─ 17 ─►|◄── 33 ──►|\n\nAnswer: Product = 561 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
