      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1899,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "If 2 is added to the numerator and 3 to the denominator of\na fraction it becomes 3/4. If 3 is subtracted from the\nnumerator and 2 from the denominator it becomes 1/3. Find\nthe fraction.",
