    },
    {
      "id": "el_81",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1964,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let (a-2), a, (a+2)\n  (a-2)²+a²+(a+2)²=440 → 3a²+8=440\n  a²=144 → a=12. Numbers: 10,12,14\nStep 2: Check: 100+144+196=440✓\n\nTRICK (expansion formula):\n3 consecutive (gap=d): 3a²+2d²=sum\nHere d=2: 3a²+8=440→a²=144→a=12\n\n  10 ── 12 ── 14\n    +2    +2\n\nAnswer: 10, 12, 14 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
